{
  "stem": "9262.7",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then we were given coffee, some sort of coffee.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And those who had something to eat, ate.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If you had nothing to eat, you didn't eat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were marching out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I was in a commando, which went to do bomb disposals.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Like, they bombed a place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we had to go and look what happened.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If any people were still underneath, we had to dug them out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if there was anything else, like, we had to take bricks-- put bricks in-- on a special place, brick to brick, and iron to iron, and metal to metal.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if we found any clothes, you know, or if we found any bodies, we had to take them out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then somebody would come, certify.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this went on and on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, we were already told, by one of the friendly guards-- well, I say friendly guards, well, among the criminals, there was maybe somebody was a little bit more friendly than the others.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he said, boys, no pilfering.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "No thieving.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If you go back to camp, and if we find anything, you will be shot.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You will be a dead chicken.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I'm warning you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So those who believed in fate wouldn't go back with a carrot or a turnip or a potato because it was theft.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They would be shot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyway, I never-- never dreamt of ever taking anything back to camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If I found anything, I ate it straightaway, raw.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't ask about cooking a potato.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If you found a potato, you ate it raw.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You didn't hide it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You didn't look for any cooking facilities, and so on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyway, we stayed at Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And every day was something different.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People were hanged-- Is that Auschwitz, or--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People were hanged.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
